'''[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]'''是一位[[美國|美國]]男導演、製片人兼演員。貝的職業生涯從執導[[MV|MV]]和商業廣告開始，其中包括贏得{{le|克里奧國際廣告獎|Clio Awards}}的1992年[[美國紅十字會|美國紅十字會]]廣告<ref name="AMC">{{cite web|url=http://www.amctv.com/originals/shootout/smso_guests/biopage_bay|title=Michael Bay|work=[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC]]|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100622075558/http://www.amctv.com/originals/shootout/smso_guests/biopage_bay|archive-date=2010-06-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、1993年[[牛奶|牛奶]]廣告片《{{le|亞倫·伯 (廣告)|Aaron Burr (advertisement)|亞倫·伯}}》<ref name="SFGate(2012-01-28)">{{cite web|url=https://www.sfgate.com/business/article/Popular-Got-Milk-ad-to-return-Recycling-of-2798935.php|title=Popular 'Got Milk?' ad to return / Recycling of 'Aaron Burr' is unusual among TV commercials|last=Raine|first=George|work=[[舊金山紀事報|San Francisco Chronicle]]|date=2012-01-28|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831113133/https://www.sfgate.com/business/article/Popular-Got-Milk-ad-to-return-Recycling-of-2798935.php|archive-date=2019-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及[[唐尼·奧斯蒙|唐尼·奧斯蒙]]、[[冥河合唱團|冥河合唱團]]和[[肉塊合唱團|肉塊合唱團]]歌曲的MV<ref name="IMVDb">{{cite web|url=https://imvdb.com/n/michael-bay|title=Michael Bay - Videography|work=IMVDb|accessdate=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809022538/https://imvdb.com/n/michael-bay|archive-date=2020-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。憑藉商業廣告出名的貝受到電影製片人[[傑瑞·布洛克海默|傑瑞·布洛克海默]]的賞識而開始接觸電影界；貝執導的首部電影為1995年[[動作片|動作]][[喜劇片|喜劇片]]《[[絕地戰警|絕地戰警]]》，該片的成功使主演[[威爾·史密斯|威爾·史密斯]]和[[馬丁·勞倫斯|馬丁·勞倫斯]]成為著名的動作影星<ref name="AMC" />。1994年，貝憑他在廣告界的成就而贏得[[美国导演工会奖|美国导演工会奖]]<ref name="1994DGA">{{cite web|url=http://www.dga.org/Awards/History/1990s/1994.aspx|title=Honoring Outstanding Directorial Achievement for 1994|work=[[美国导演工会奖|Directors Guild of America]]|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801075806/http://www.dga.org/Awards/History/1990s/1994.aspx|archive-date=2020-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。貝的第二部電影作品為[[尼可拉斯·凱吉|尼可拉斯·凱吉]]及[[史恩·康納萊|史恩·康納萊]]主演的動作片《[[絕地任務|絕地任務]]》（1996年），該片口碑良好且在全球獲得超過3.35億美元的成功票房<ref name="BOM(TheRock)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3211560449/|title=The Rock (1996)|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907194315/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3211560449/|archive-date=2020-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後，他的[[科幻片|科幻]][[災難片|災難片]]《[[絕世天劫|絕世天劫]]》為1998年票房最高的電影<ref name="BOM(1998)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/1998/|title=Domestic Box Office For 1998|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029024911/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/1998/|archive-date=2020-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《絕世天劫》的成功使貝獲得了{{le|土星獎最佳導演|Saturn Award for Best Director}}<ref name="Variety(1999-06-15)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1999/film/news/sci-fi-acad-sends-pix-into-orbit-with-saturns-1117503072/|title=Sci-fi acad sends pix into orbit with Saturns|last=Chang|first=Kay|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=1999-06-15|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915121938/https://variety.com/1999/film/news/sci-fi-acad-sends-pix-into-orbit-with-saturns-1117503072/|archive-date=2018-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時晉升為全球票房累計10億美元的年輕導演行列<ref name="Esquire(2013-04-26)">{{cite web|url=https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/a22376/michael-bay-profile-2001/|title=Bay|last=Laskas|first=Jeanne Marie|work=[[时尚先生_(刊物)|Esquire]]|date=2013-04-26|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807125359/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/a22376/michael-bay-profile-2001/|archive-date=2020-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="THR(2014-06-19)">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-bay-scored-pearl-harbor-712425|title=Throwback Thursday: Michael Bay Scored With 'Pearl Harbor' in 2001|last=Higgins|first=Bill|work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-06-19|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809103131/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-bay-scored-pearl-harbor-712425|archive-date=2020-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

三年後，貝執導兼監製了[[戰爭片|戰爭片]]《[[珍珠港_(電影)|珍珠港]]》（2001年），雖然評價兩極<ref name="(2001-05-21)">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1351948.stm|title=US critics take aim at Pearl Harbor|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|BBC News]]|date=2001-05-21|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807104145/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1351948.stm|archive-date=2020-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但全球票房則超過4.49億美元<ref name="BOM(PearlHarbor)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl543720961/|title=Pearl Harbor (2001)|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807150641/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl543720961/|archive-date=2020-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，貝和[[安德魯·福姆|安德魯·福姆]]與[[布萊德·富勒_(製片人)|布萊德·福勒]]創立了自己的製片公司[[白金沙丘|白金沙丘]]，旨在製作預算較低的電影，貝也會在其製作的項目中擔任監製<ref name="AMC" /><ref name="Variety(2002-03-03)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2002/film/news/o-seas-distribs-rev-up-chainsaw-redo-1117861734/|title=O’seas distribs rev up ‘Chainsaw’ redo|last=Harris|first=Dana|work=Variety|date=2002-03-03|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915084621/https://variety.com/2002/film/news/o-seas-distribs-rev-up-chainsaw-redo-1117861734/|archive-date=2018-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。貝之後推出了《絕地戰警》的續集《[[絕地戰警2|絕地戰警2]]》，史密斯和勞倫斯皆回歸出演各自的角色<ref name="BadBoysII(NYTimes)">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/279009/Bad-Boys-II/cast|title=Bad Boys II (2003)|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306183456/https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/279009/Bad-Boys-II/cast|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。兩年後，他執導了科幻動作片《[[絕地再生|絕地再生]]》（2005年），但卻獲得了失敗的口碑及票房<ref name="Slate(2006-02-06)">{{cite news|url=https://slate.com/culture/2006/02/why-the-island-failed-at-the-box-office.html|title=The End of Originality|last=Epstein|first=Edward Jay|work=[[Slate_(雜誌)|Slate]]|date=2006-02-06|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804124328/https://slate.com/culture/2006/02/why-the-island-failed-at-the-box-office.html|archive-date=2020-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

貝從2007年起開始執導真人版《[[变形金刚电影系列|變形金剛]]》電影系列，[[變形金剛_(2007年電影)|首部電影]]在商業上取得成功，全球票房收入超過7.09億美元<ref name="BOM(Transformers)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3010954753/|title=Transformers (2007)|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019085600/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3010954753/|archive-date=2020-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，他的《[[變形金剛：復仇之戰|變形金剛：復仇之戰]]》（2009年）雖然評價不佳，但其票房仍高達8.36億美元<ref name="BOM(Transformers:RevengeoftheFallen)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3027731969/|title=Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen (2009)|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022000735/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl3027731969/|archive-date=2020-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，貝執導了系列第三部電影《[[變形金剛3|變形金剛3]]》，該片在全球獲得11.24億美元的成功票房<ref name="BOM(Transformers:DarkoftheMoon)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2977400321/|title=Transformers: Dark of the Moon (2011)|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828221402/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl2977400321/|archive-date=2020-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩年後，貝執導兼監製了成本不高的[[犯罪片|犯罪]][[喜劇片|喜劇片]]《[[不勞而禍|不勞而禍]]》（2013年）<ref name="Variety(2013-04-22)">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/pain-gain-review-1200391657/|title=Film Review: ‘Pain & Gain’|last=Foundas|first=Scott|work=Variety|date=2013-04-22|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200428042600/https://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/pain-gain-review-1200391657/|archive-date=2020-04-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，貝回歸《變形金剛》系列、執導了《[[變形金剛4：絕跡重生|變形金剛4：絕跡重生]]》，全球票房超過11億美元，成為當年全球票房收入最高的電影<ref name="BOM(2014)">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/2014/|title=Domestic Box Office For 2014|work=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017012342/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/year/2014/|archive-date=2020-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。貝於2016年帶來了執導的軍事動作驚悚片《[[13小時：班加西的秘密士兵|13小時：班加西的秘密士兵]]》<ref name="Variety(2016-01-13)">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/13-hours-review-michael-bay-benghazi-1201679100/|title=Film Review: ‘13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi’|last=Chang|first=Justin|work=Variety|date=2016-01-13|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013202211/https://variety.com/2016/film/reviews/13-hours-review-michael-bay-benghazi-1201679100/|archive-date=2020-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，他執導了《[[變形金剛5：最終騎士|變形金剛5：最終騎士]]》，口碑不佳且票房也不如前幾部<ref name="TheIndependent(2017-06-21)">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/transformers-5-last-knight-new-film-reviews-round-michael-bay-mark-wahlberg-anthony-hopkins-a7800076.html|title=Transformers 5: Reviews round-up as The Last Knight hits cinemas|last=Stolworthy|first=Jacob|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2017-06-21|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907175527/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/transformers-5-last-knight-new-film-reviews-round-michael-bay-mark-wahlberg-anthony-hopkins-a7800076.html|archive-date=2020-09-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。貝的下一部執導作為動作片《[[鬼影特攻：以暴制暴|鬼影特攻：以暴制暴]]》，2019年上線[[Netflix|Netflix]]，很快地受到該平台觀眾的歡迎<ref name="THR(2020-01-21)">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/6-underground-viewed-by-83-million-members-netflix-says-1271794|title=Michael Bay's '6 Underground' Viewed by 83 Million Members, Netflix Says|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2020-01-21|accessdate=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919063427/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/6-underground-viewed-by-83-million-members-netflix-says-1271794|archive-date=2020-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年，動作驚悚片《[[劫命救護|劫命救護]]》雖然口碑褒貶不一，但仍在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]網站上取得69%的新鮮度，成為貝繼《絕地任務》後第二部獲得「新鮮」認證的執導作<ref name="AmbulanceRT">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ambulance|title=Ambulance (2022)|work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]]|accessdate=2022-04-22}}</ref>。

